# Kill-criteria telemetry (REQ-008-09).
#
# Runtime events are written by scripts/metrics/kill_criteria.py to
# drift-events.jsonl in this directory. That file is git-ignored; this
# .gitkeep seed keeps the directory present on a fresh clone so the
# emitter never has to create a tracked path. See
# .agents/specs/requirements/REQ-008-review-axes-convergence.md (K1-K4).
